Package: cara
Type: Package
Title: Draw and Manipulate Images with Cairo
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mike", "Cheng", role = c("aut", "cre", 'cph'), email = "mikefc@coolbutuseless.com")
    )
Maintainer: Mike Cheng <mikefc@coolbutuseless.com>
Description: Functions for low-level manipulation and drawing with images supported by
    the 'Cairo' library.  Direct access to 'Cairo' drawing surfaces for image
    creating, shape drawing, text rendering, pattern rendering, and image copying.  Supports 
    masked operations and configuration of core options such as antialiasing, 
    filtering and pattern handling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
SystemRequirements:
    cairo (>= 1.2 http://www.cairographics.org/),
    freetype2,
    fontconfig
LinkingTo: colorfast
Imports:
    colorfast (>= 1.0.1.9000)
Suggests: 
    png,
    magick,
    knitr,
    systemfonts,
    textshaping,
    rmarkdown,
    vdiffr,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Remotes:
    coolbutuseless/colorfast
